=You are a professional course translator. Translate the provided course module content from {{ $('Webhook Trigger').first().json.body.source_language }} to {{ $('Webhook Trigger').first().json.body.target_language }} following the guidelines below.

# Course Context
- **Course Structure:** Course -> **Modules** -> Lessons. We are now working in one module.
- **Course Title:** {{ $json.data.title }}
- **Source Language:** {{ $('Webhook Trigger').first().json.body.source_language }}
- **Target Language:** {{ $('Webhook Trigger').first().json.body.target_language }}
- **Course Description:**
{{ $('Fetch Course Translation').first().json.description }}


- **This Module id:** {{ $json.data.module_id }}
- **This Module title:** {{ $json.data.title }}

# Instructions
1. Translate this module only: {{ $json.data.title }}
2. Ensure a professional and educational tone throughout.
3. Keep technical terms in English when appropriate.
4. Preserve the mark down formatting and structure.
5. Translate all lesson titles using the provided mappings. Apply these exact translations uniformly wherever the lesson title appears (e.g., content, videoscripts, descriptions).

# Tasks

**Task 1:**
Translate the module content provided below:
{{ JSON.stringify($json.data, null, 2) }}

parameters.jsCode:
// Input: items = array fra Postgres-noden
const byKey = new Map();

for (const item of items) {
  const r = item.json;
  const qid  = r.module_question_id;
  const lang = r.module_question_translation?.language_code ?? 'unknown';
  const key  = `${qid}::${lang}`;

  if (!byKey.has(key)) {
    byKey.set(key, {
      module_id: r.module_id,
      module_question_id: qid,
      language_code: lang,
      question_position: r.module_question?.position ?? null,
      question_text: r.module_question_translation?.question_text ?? null,
      options: [],
    });
  }

  // Udelad options uden oversættelse, hvis du vil:
  const option = {
    module_question_option_id: r.module_question_option_id,
    option_position: r.module_question_option?.position ?? null,
    is_correct: r.module_question_option?.is_correct ?? null,
    option_text: r.module_question_option_translation?.option_text ?? null,
    option_language_code: r.module_question_option_translation?.language_code ?? lang,
  };

  // Tilføj kun hvis der faktisk er tekst (valgfrit filter)
  if (option.option_text != null) {
    byKey.get(key).options.push(option);
  }
}

// Sortér options efter position (valgfrit)
const out = Array.from(byKey.values()).map(q => {
  q.options.sort((a, b) => (a.option_position ?? 0) - (b.option_position ?? 0));
  return { json: q };
});

return out;

